{{Quote|He calls me his 'little mom'.|Ardees Rabang on Rick McCallum|<ref name="Making">''[[The Making of Star Wars Revenge of the Sith]]'', p. 216-217</ref>}}
'''Ardees Rabang Jundis''' was an "assistant to controller" for [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]<ref name="Episode I Cast and Crew">{{SWArchive|url=episode-i/bts/castcrew.html|text=Episode I Cast and Crew}}</ref> and was one of two US Assistants to [[Rick McCallum]] during the production of [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']]<ref name="Episode II Cast and Crew">{{SWArchive|url=episode-ii/bts/castcrew.html|text=Episode II Cast and Crew}}</ref> and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']].<ref name="Making" />

She later served as assistant to McCallum again for [[George Lucas]]' 2012 film [[Wikipedia:Red Tails|''Red Tails'']].

The beverage [[Ardees/Legends|ardees]] was named after her.<ref name="Databank: WA-7 (Behind the scenes)">{{DB|droid|wa7|FLO (WA-7)}}</ref>

